[This is the FDA recall notice from several days ago related to the
dog food. It should be noted that 23 of the 66 (35 percent) CDC
reported _S._ Schwarzengrund outbreak strain cases were in states not
listed for distribution of the canine food. The distribution of the
food was limited to the northeastern part of the country, but cases
have been reported from Ohio, Maine, North Dakota, Virginia,
Minnesota, Alabama, California, Delaware, Illinois, Kentucky,
Maryland, Michigan, North Carolina, and Wisconsin. Unless the cases
have links to the distribution states, other company products not yet
recalled are likely involved. - Mod.LL]
